There is MSVC 6.0 project that in the source directory. Scitech and DirectX SDK 
libs and headers are not included as they can be taken from the original Quake 
sources or from Microsoft. The libpng, zlib, libjpeg libraries and 
corresponding headers can be downloaded here: http://2wp.vei.ru/files/libs.rar
Put the content of the archive into source/lib directory.

MinGW and Cygwin can also be used. Run ./configure and make.
